            "type": "hardBreak"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Implement a separate service that consumes bet events, stores the latest N bets in cache, filters bets based on min/max settings, and publishes filtered events via WebSockets. The service must include product information in the response to support game navigation on the UI."
          }
